=\"SE-3c669617-c25e-4df4-9f9e-41e4ebe8a2a1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b654b1bc-1ed5-4192-9263-bc7c667b6990\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-file se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e7928358-01b9-4277-9341-37f1719d7321\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-file se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-file\">\n<span class=\"se-file-icon\"><strong class=\"se-blind\">첨부파일</strong></span>\n<div class=\"se-file-name-container\">\n<span class=\"se-file-name\">2023 (주)파파스컴퍼니 새해인사</span><span class=\"se-file-extension\">.mp4</span>\n</div>\n<a class=\"se-file-save-button __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"link\": \"https://download.blog.naver.com/open/5bce47f7e5b9bf634ea1c9fccd23512780d72ec68e/EFsQbrdLxLvO9t9eLuoSggWaFwbSq-dpeF8XKG00xEFxTtTRU3sh7ve9CIVljSkkqyT2f2CmvAw-3AsATEVir6F7jkq9Yao5uqoRGA/2023%20%EC%BF%A1%EB%8D%94%EB%94%94%EC%9E%90%EC%9D%B8%20%EC%83%88%ED%95%B4%EC%9D%B8%EC%82%AC.mp4\"}' data-linktype=\"file\" href=\"https://download.blog.naver.com/open/5bce47f7e5b9bf634ea1c9fccd23512780d72ec68e/EFsQbrdLxLvO9t9eLuoSggWaFwbSq-dpeF8XKG00xEFxTtTRU3sh7ve9CIVljSkkqyT2f2CmvAw-3AsATEVir6F7jkq9Yao5uqoRGA/2023%20%EC%BF%A1%EB%8D%94%EB%94%94%EC%9E%90%EC%9D%B8%20%EC%83%88%ED%95%B4%EC%9D%B8%EC%82%AC.mp4\" role=\"button\" target=\"_blank\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">파일 다운로드</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-09130c5f-5805-4d8e-b2f7-907a43853812\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c1873309-9d93-44ef-b713-a826c5f03858\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"s